ani k’a to mobili kɔnɔ....”
“O mobili ye kura ye, a ma sigi a kelen na....”
Dudley y’a daminɛ ka kasi kosɛbɛ. Tiɲɛ na, a tun tɛ kasi tiɲɛ na — a tun bɛ kasi
