SABABU SABANAN
LƐTƐW MINNU BƐ BƆ MƆGƆ SI LA
T he escape of the Brezil boa constrictor ye Harry sɔrɔ a ka waati janba la
ɲangili. Waati min na u y’a to a ka bɔ a ka kabini tugun, o ye samiyɛ ye
seliw tun daminɛna ani Dudley tun y' a ka videyo kamera kura tiɲɛ kaban ,
a y’a ka yɔrɔjan kunnafoni-di-aviyɔn gosi, wa, a siɲɛ fɔlɔ min bɔra a ka boli-nɛgɛso kan, .
ye Madamu Figg kɔrɔba gosi k’a to Privet Drive tɛmɛtɔ a ka berew kan.
Harry nisɔndiyara ko lakɔli banna, nka mɔgɔ si tun tɛ yen min bɛ se ka boli Dudley ta la
gang, minnu tun bɛ taa bɔ so kɔnɔ don o don. Piers, Dennis, Malcolm ani
Gordon bɛɛ tun ye mɔgɔba ye ani nalomanw, nka iko Dudley tun ye mɔgɔba ye ani hakilintan ye
kalata , ale de tun ye ɲɛmɔgɔ ye . U tɔw bɛɛ nisɔndiyara kosɛbɛ ka fara u kan
Dudley ka farikoloɲɛnajɛ min ka di a ye kosɛbɛ: Harry Hunting.
O de y’a to Harry ye waati caman kɛ ka bɔ so kɔnɔ,
yaala-yaala ka miiri seliw laban na , a tun bɛ se ka ye yɔrɔ min na
jigiya yeelen fitinin dɔ. Sɛtanburukalo sera tuma min na a tun bɛ taa seginkanni na
lakɔli la ani, a siɲɛ fɔlɔ don a ka ɲɛnamaya kɔnɔ, a tun tɛna kɛ Dudley fɛ. Dudley tun ye o kɛ
sɔnna Uncle Vernon ka lakɔliso kɔrɔ la, n’o ye Smeltings ye. Piers Polkiss tun ye o ye
ka taa yen fana. Harry kɔni tun bɛ taa Stonewall High la, o ye sigida la
foroba lakɔliso. Dudley tun b’a miiri ko nin ye nisɔndiyako ye kosɛbɛ.
A ko: “U bɛ mɔgɔw kunkolow don ɲɛgɛn kɔnɔ tile fɔlɔ la Stonewall
a y'o fɔ Harry ye. “I b’a fɛ ka na sanfɛ ka dege wa?”
Harry ko: “Ayi, barika Ala ye. “Wulilan faantanw ma deli ka foyi sɔrɔ i n’a fɔ
a ka jugu i n’a fɔ i kunkolo bɛ jigin a la cogo min na — a bɛ se ka kɛ bana ye.” O kɔ, a bolila, Dudley ɲɛfɛ
tun bɛ se ka baara kɛ a ye min fɔ.
Don dɔ la, Zuluyekalo la, tantan Petunia taara ni Dudley ye Lɔnduru walasa k’a ta san
Smeltings ka fini, ka Harry to Madamu Figg ka so. Madamu Figg tun man jugu i n’a fɔ
kɔrɔlen. A y'a Sɔrɔ a y'a sen kari k'a Blà a ka misi dɔ kan, wa ale
a tun bɛ iko u tun man di u ye kosɛbɛ i n’a fɔ fɔlɔ. A y’a to Harry ka telewisɔn filɛ ani...
ye sokola gato dɔɔnin di a ma min tun bɛ i n’a fɔ a y’a sɔrɔ kabini damadɔ
sanw.
O wulada fɛ, Dudley ye parade kɛ ka denbaya lamini so kɔnɔ
a ka fini kura yɛrɛyɛrɛ. Smeltings cɛdenw tun bɛ wuluwuluw don minnu ye maroon ye, oranjɛ
knickerbockers, ani bɔgɔdaga fla minnu bɛ wele ko kurunbokarilaw. U tun bɛ knobbly fana ta
berew , minnu bɛ kɛ ka ɲɔgɔn gosi k' a sɔrɔ karamɔgɔw ma filɛli kɛ . Nin tun ye nin ye
a ka kan ka kɛ degeliw ɲuman ye ɲɛnamaya kɔfɛ.
A kɛlen ka Dudley filɛ a ka knickerbockers kura kɔnɔ, Uncle Vernon y’o fɔ
ni kɔnɔnafili ye k’a fɔ ko o kɛra a ka ɲɛnamaya kɔnɔ waso waati ye min ka bon ni waati tɔw bɛɛ ye. Tante Petunia ye kasi kɛ
ani ko a ma se ka da a la ko a ka Ickle Dudleykins de don, a ɲɛda tun bɛ ten
cɛɲi ani mɔgɔkɔrɔba. Harry ma da a yɛrɛ la ka kuma. A ye miiri fila la
a kɔkiliw tun bɛ se ka kari kaban k’a sababu kɛ a y’a ɲini a kana ŋɛɲɛ.
* * * .
Kasa jugu dɔ bɔra dumunikɛyɔrɔ la o dugujɛ, Harry taara tuma min na
in ka sɔgɔmada dumuni kɛ. A tun bɛ iko a tun bɛ bɔ nɛgɛdaga belebele dɔ la min tun bɛ jisigiyɔrɔ la. A
taara a lajɛ. O jidagayɔrɔ tun falen bɛ fɛnw na minnu tun bɛ i n’a fɔ fini nɔgɔlenw minnu bɛ ka jigin ka don a kɔnɔ
ji jɛman.
“Nin ye mun ye?” a ye tantan Petunia ɲininka. A dawolo gɛlɛyara i n’a fɔ a tun bɛ kɛ cogo min na tuma bɛɛ
y' a kɛ n' a y' a ja gɛlɛya ka ɲininkali kɛ .
A ko: “I ka lakɔli fini kura.
Harry ye a ɲɛw lajɛ daga kɔnɔ tugun.
A ko: “O, ne tun t’a dɔn ko a ka kan ka jigin ten.”
Tante Petunia y’a fɔ ni kɔnɔnafili ye ko: “I kana kɛ naloman ye. “Ne bɛ ka Dudley ta dɔw kala
fɛn kɔrɔw gris ye aw ye. A bɛna kɛ i n’a fɔ mɔgɔ tɔw bɛɛ ta dɔrɔn, ni ne ye baara kɛ ka ban.”
Harry tun bɛ sigasiga kosɛbɛ o la, nka a y’a miiri ko a ka fisa a kana sɔsɔli kɛ. A y'i sigi
duguma tabali la k'a ɲini a kana miiri a bɛna a ta cogo min na
tile fɔlɔ Stonewall High la — i n’a fɔ a tun bɛ waraba fari kɔrɔ dɔw don,
a bɛ se ka kɛ.
Dudley ni Uncle Vernon donna, u fila bɛɛ nugu kurulen don k’a sababu kɛ
kasa min bɔra Harry ka fini kura la. Uncle Vernon y’a ka kunnafonisɛbɛn da wuli iko
a delila ka kɛ ani Dudley y’a ka Smelting bere gosi, a tun bɛ min ta yɔrɔ bɛɛ, a kan
tabali kan.
U ye lɛtɛrɛw ciyɔrɔ digi ani lɛtɛrɛw ka flop mɛn da la.
Uncle Vernon y’a fɔ ka bɔ a ka papier kɔfɛ ko: “I ka lɛtɛrɛ ta, Dudley.”
“A to Harry k’a sɔrɔ.”
“I ka lɛtɛrɛ sɔrɔ, Harry.”
“A to Dudley k’a sɔrɔ.”
“A poyi n’i ka Smelting bere ye, Dudley.”
Harry y’a yɛrɛ tanga Smelting bere ma, ka taa lɛtɛrɛ ta. Fɛn saba
a dalen bɛ da la : karti dɔ bɔra Uncle Vernon balimamuso Marge fɛ, min tun bɛ
lafiɲɛbɔ la Wight gun kan, anwɛlɛki bulama dɔ min tun bɛ i n’a fɔ warisɛbɛn, ani —
bataki dɔ min dira Harry ma.
Harry y’a ta k’a filɛ ni ɲɛmajɔ ye, a dusukun bɛ ka wuli i n’a fɔ elastik belebeleba
bandi. Mɔgɔ si, abada, a ka ɲɛnamaya bɛɛ kɔnɔ, tun ma sɛbɛn ci a ma. Jɔn tun bɛna o kɛ? A tun tɛ ni foyi ye
teriw, somɔgɔw wɛrɛw tɛ — a tun tɛ gafemarayɔrɔ ta ye, o la a tun tɛna hali abada
ye sɛbɛnw sɔrɔ minnu bɛ kɛ ni maloya ye k’a ɲini gafew fɛ ka segin. O bɛɛ n’a ta, a tun bɛ yan, bataki, min ɲɛsinnen bɛ ten
a jɛlen don ko fili tun tɛ se ka kɛ:
