dumunikɛyɔrɔ la ani a seginna tuma min na, lɛtɛrɛ sera, ka don Uncle kɔnɔ yɛrɛ
Vernon ka lap. Harry tun bɛ se ka bataki saba ye minnu ɲɛsinnen bɛ ni tintiri jɛman ye.
A y’a daminɛ ko: “Ne b’a fɛ —,” nka Uncle Vernon tun bɛ ka batakiw tigɛtigɛ
yɔrɔw bɛ a ɲɛ kɔrɔ.
Uncle Vernon ma taa baara la o don. A tora so kɔnɔ ka nɛgɛso tigɛ
ka taa lɛtɛrɛw bilayɔrɔ la.
