sɛgɛnnen ani bana dɔɔnin, nka nisɔndiya.
A y’u hakili jigin ni nisɔndiya ye k’a to a jɛnsɛnni na ko: “Posi tɛ dimansiladonw na.”
marmalade kan a ka kunnafonidisɛbɛnw kan, “no damn letters today —” .
Fɛn dɔ nana ka sɔgɔsɔgɔ ka jigin dumunikɛyɔrɔ la k’a to kuma na ani
