Cɛ Potter kanulen,
An nisɔndiyara k’aw ladɔnniya ko aw sɔnna Hogwarts
Lagbɛri ni lagbɛri kalanso. Aw ye fɛn bɛɛ lajɛlen lisɛli sɔrɔ min bɛ a kɔnɔ
gafew ni minɛnw.
Waati bɛ daminɛ sɛtanburukalo tile 1. An bɛ i ka wulu makɔnɔ a tɛ tɛmɛ Zuluyekalo tile 31 kan.
Aw ka ni kɔnɔnajɛya ye,
Minɛrva McGonagall, san 1999.
Karamɔgɔba kɔrɔsigi
Ɲininkaliw pɛrɛnna Harry kunkolo kɔnɔ i n’a fɔ tasuma-fɛrɛ ani a ma se
a latigɛ i bɛna min ɲininka fɔlɔ. Miniti damadɔ tɛmɛnen kɔfɛ a ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ ko: “A bɛ mun kɛ
kɔrɔ ye ko u bɛ ne ka wulu makɔnɔ wa?”
