HOGWARTS SCHOOL min bɛ ƝƐNABƆLI ni ƝƐNABƆLI LA
TENI
San fɔlɔ kalandenw bɛna a ɲini:
1. Baarakɛ fini gansan saba (nɛrɛma) .
2. Filɛri gansan kelen (nɛrɛma) tile donta kama
3. Ganti kelen min bɛ mɔgɔ tanga (dragon dogo walima a ɲɔgɔnna) .
4. Tilemana fini kelen (fɛn nɛrɛma, warijɛ sirilanw) .
Aw k’a kɔlɔsi ko kalandenw ka finiw bɛɛ ka kan ka kɛ ni tɔgɔsɛbɛnw ye
KƆRƆSI GAFƐNW
Kalandenw bɛɛ ka kan ka nin fɛn ninnu kelen-kelen bɛɛ kopi sɔrɔ:
Gafe min bɛ wele ko Standard Book of Spells (Kalanso fɔlɔ) min sɛbɛnna Miranda Goshawk fɛ
Maji ka tariku dɔ min sɛbɛnna Bathilda Bagshot fɛ
Teori majigi ye Adalbert Waffling fɛ
Gafe min bɛ daminɛbagaw ka fɛn caman tigɛli kan Emeric Switch fɛ
Ba kelen majigin furabuluw ni ɲɛgɛnw fɛ Phyllida Spore fɛ
Magic Drafts ani Potions ye Arsenius Jigger ka baara ye
Bagan kabakomaw ani u bɛ sɔrɔ yɔrɔ min na Newt Scamander fɛ
Dibi fanga: Yɛrɛ lakanani gafe min sɛbɛnna Quentin Trimble fɛ
MINƐN WƐRƐW
1 bere
1 daga (pewutɛri, hakɛ dantigɛlen 2) .
1 galasi walima kristalɛ fiyɛli kulu 1
1 teleskɔpu seti
1 nɛgɛso balansi
