ka segin ka don kogo gɛlɛn na.
Tile tun bɛ yeelen bɔ kosɛbɛ dagaw kulu dɔ kan, butiki min tun ka surun aw la, o kɔfɛ.
Cauldrons — Bonya bɛɛ — Kupu, Nɛgɛ, Pewu, Warijɛ — Yɛrɛ-yɛrɛ-yɛrɛ —
Collapsible, taamasiyɛn dɔ min sirilen bɛ u kan, o y’o fɔ.
