fɔlɔ."
Harry tun b’a fɛ ɲɛ 8 ɲɔgɔn wɛrɛ ka sɔrɔ a la. A y'a kunkolo Yɛlɛma o bɛɛ la
siratigɛ la u bɛ taama ka wuli nbɛda la , k' a ɲini ka fɛn bɛɛ lajɛ siɲɛ kelen : o
butikiw , fɛn minnu bɛ u kɔkan , mɔgɔw b' u ka sanni kɛ . Muso fasalen dɔ
kɛnɛma Furakɛla dɔ tun bɛ k’a kunkolo wuli u tɛmɛtɔ, k’a fɔ ko: “Dragon
sugunɛ, Siki tan ni wolonwula onsi kelen na, u bɛ dimi....”
Hooting dɔgɔmannin dɔ bɔra dibi butiki dɔ la, taamasiyɛn dɔ tun bɛ min kan ko Eeylops
Owl Emporium — Tawny, Screech, Barn, Brown ani Snowy. Cɛden damadɔw ka...
Harry si hakɛ ɲɔgɔnna, u nuguw tun bɛ digi finɛtiri dɔ kan ni bɔrɔw ye minnu kɔnɔ
a. “A filɛ,” Harry y’u dɔ ka kuma mɛn, “Nimbus Two Thousand kura — .
fastest ever —” Butigi dɔw tun bɛ yen minnu tun bɛ finiw feere, butiki minnu tun bɛ teleskɔpu feere ani
warijɛ fɔlifɛn kabakoma minnu Harry tun ma deli ka minnu ye fɔlɔ, finɛtiriw falen bɛ ɲɔgɔn na
batɛmuw ni wuluw ɲɛw bariliw, siginiden gafew kuluw, quills, ani
pargamin rollow, fura buteliw, kalo globow....
Hagrid ko: “Gringotts.
U tun sera boon finman dɔ la, nɛnɛ tun bɛ min kɔnɔ, o tun ka bon ka tɛmɛ tɔ kelen kan
butiki fitininw. A jɔlen a ka nɛgɛdaga jɛlenw kɛrɛfɛ, a bɛ fini don min na
bilenman ni sanu, tun ye —
“Ɔwɔ, o ye goblin ye,” Hagrid y’o fɔ ni dususuma ye k’u to taama na ka wuli fini jɛman kan
kabakurun bɛ senna ka taa a fan fɛ. Goblin tun ka surun ni Harry ye ni kunkolo kelen ɲɔgɔn ye. A tun ye o kɛ
ɲɛda nɛrɛmuguma, hakilitigi, kunsigi nɛrɛmuguma ani, Harry y’a kɔlɔsi, bolokɔnincinin janba ani
senw. A y'i biri u taamatɔ kɔnɔna na. Sisan, u tun ɲɛsinnen bɛ fila filanan ma
daaw, warijɛ nin sen in na, daɲɛw jalen bɛ u kan:
Don, dunan, nka i k'i janto
Fɛn min bɛ namara jurumu makɔnɔ, .
Minnu bɛ fɛn ta, nka u tɛ wari sɔrɔ,
Ka kan ka sara ka tɛmɛ tɔw bɛɛ kan u ka waati la.
O la ni aw ye ɲinini kɛ an ka dugumalanw jukɔrɔ
Nafolo min tun tɛ i ta ye abada,
Son, i lasɔmina, i k'i janto
Ka fɛn caman sɔrɔ yen ka tɛmɛ nafolo kan.
Hagrid ko: “I n’a fɔ ne y’a fɔ cogo min na, Yeh’d be mad ter try an’ rob it.”
Goblin fila y'u biri warijɛ daaw fɛ ani u tun bɛ a kɔnɔ
marbre ka soba belebeleba dɔ. Goblin kɛmɛ ɲɔgɔn wɛrɛw tun sigilen bɛ sigilan sanfɛtaw kan
jatebɔlan jan dɔ kɔfɛ, a bɛ sɛbɛnni kɛ gafe belebelebaw kɔnɔ, ka warijɛw pese nɛgɛso balansi kɔnɔ,
kabakurun nafamaw sɛgɛsɛgɛli ɲɛkisɛw fɛ. Da caman tun ka ca kojugu
jate min bɛ taa ka bɔ boon kɔnɔ, o bɛɛ n’a ta, goblin caman tun bɛ ka mɔgɔw jira ka don ani ka bɔ
ninnu la. Hagrid ni Harry ye u kɛ ka taa jatebɔyɔrɔ la.
