HP 1 - Harry Potter ni a ka
Lagbɛrikɛla ka Kabakurun
SABABU SABABU
TAAMA MIN BƐ KA BƆ PLATEFORM KƆNƆ NI SABA KAN
H arry ka kalo laban ni Dursleyw ma diya. Tiɲɛ don, Dudley tun bɛ ten sisan
siran Harry ɲɛ a tɛna to so kelen kɔnɔ, k'a sɔrɔ tantan Petunia ni
Uncle Vernon ma Harry datugu a ka kabini kɔnɔ, k’a wajibiya ka foyi kɛ, walima
pɛrɛn a kan — tiɲɛ yɛrɛ la, u ma kuma a fɛ fewu. Tila kelen sirannen don, tilancɛ
u dimina kosɛbɛ, u y’a kɛ i n’a fɔ sigilan o sigilan min bɛ Harry kɔnɔ, o lankolon don. Hali
nin kɛra ɲɛtaa ye cogo caman na, a kɛra degun ye dɔɔnin a kɔfɛ
ka .... to.
Harry tora a ka so kɔnɔ, n’a ka wulu kura ye jɛɲɔgɔnya kama. A tun y’a latigɛ k’o kɛ
a wele ko Hedwig, tɔgɔ min tun bɛ a bolo A History of Magic kɔnɔ. A ka lakɔli gafew
tun ka di kosɛbɛ. A dalen tun bɛ a ka dilan kan ka kalan kɛ fo su fɛ, Hedwig
ka don ka bɔ finɛtiri da wulilen na i n’a fɔ a b’a fɛ cogo min na. A kɛra chance ye ko Tante
Petunia ma don ka vacuum kɛ tugun, bawo Hedwig tora ka na ni a ye
soso salenw. Su o su sanni a ka sunɔgɔ, Harry tun bɛ tile wɛrɛ tigɛ
a tun ye papiye min siri kogo la, ka jate kɛ ka jigin fo sɛtanburukalo la
fɔlɔ.
Awirilikalo laban don a y'a miiri ko a ka fisa a ka kuma a kɔrɔmuso fɛ ani
uncle ka se ka se King's Cross gare ma o dugujɛ, o de la a jigira ka taa
so kɔnɔ u tun bɛ ɲininkali kɛcogo dɔ lajɛ telewisɔn na. A ye a ta saniya
dawolo la walasa u k'a dɔn ko a bɛ yen, Dudley kulela ka boli ka bɔ
soden.
“Er — Uncle Vernon wa?”
Uncle Vernon ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ k’a jira ko a bɛ ka lamɛnni kɛ.
“Er — ne ka kan ka kɛ King’s Cross la sini ka — ka taa Hogwarts.”
Uncle Vernon ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ tugun.
“Yala a bɛna ɲɛ ni i ye lifatan di ne ma wa?”
Grunt (dɔnkilida). Harry tun b’a miiri ko o kɔrɔ ye ko ɔwɔ.
"A' ni cɛ."
A tun bɛna segin sanfɛ tuma min na, Uncle Vernon kumana tiɲɛ na.
“Fɛn nisɔndiyalen don ka se lagbɛrikɛlaw ka lakɔli la, tɛrɛn. Tapis magiques bɛɛ sɔrɔla
sɔgɔsɔgɔninjɛw, wa?”
Harry ma foyi fɔ.
“Nin lakɔliso in bɛ min, cogo o cogo?”
Harry y’a fɔ ko: “Ne t’a dɔn,” a y’o faamu a siɲɛ fɔlɔ la. A ye a sama ka
tikiti Hagrid tun ye min di a ma ka bɔ a ka bɔrɛ kɔnɔ.
“Ne bɛ tɛrɛn ta dɔrɔn ka bɔ plateforme kɔnɔntɔn na ani saba tilancɛ la tan ni kelen waati
nɛgɛ kanɲɛ fɛ,” a y’o kalan.
A kɔrɔmuso n’a facɛ denkɛ y’u ɲɛ jɔlen to.
