A ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ. A lamini mɔgɔw fana y’o kɛ ten. Jinɛ mugan ɲɔgɔn tun bɛ yen dɔrɔn
a bɛ woyo ka tɛmɛ kɔfɛ kogo fɛ. Perle-finman ani transparent dɔɔni, u
u ye sɛgɛnlafiɲɛbɔ kɛ so kɔnɔ ka kuma ɲɔgɔn fɛ ani u ma ɲɛmajɔli kɛ fɔlɔ la
sanw. A tun bɛ iko u tun bɛ sɔsɔli kɛ. Fɛn min tun bɛ i n’a fɔ mɔnikɛ fitinin fasalen dɔ, o tun b’a fɔ ko:
“Yafa ani ka ɲinɛ, ne ko, an ka kan ka sababu filanan di a ma —”
