GRIFINDƆRƆ!”
Harry ye fini in mɛn a ye kuma laban pɛrɛn ka ɲɛsin boon bɛɛ ma. A ye a ka...
hat ani a taamana ni yɛrɛyɛrɛ ye ka taa Gryffindor tabali fan fɛ. A dusu saalora kosɛbɛ k’a sɔrɔ a ye o sɔrɔ
sugandira ani a ma bila Slytherin kɔnɔ, a ma kɔlɔsi kosɛbɛ ko a bɛ ka sɔrɔ
nisɔndiyakanba min ka bon kosɛbɛ hali bi. Percy the Prefect wulila k’a bolo minɛ ni fanga ye, k’a sɔrɔ
Weasley filaninw pɛrɛnna ko “An ye Potter sɔrɔ! An ye Potter sɔrɔ!” Harry y'i sigi
jinɛ kɛrɛfɛ ruff kɔnɔ a tun ye min ye ka tɛmɛ. Jinɛ y’a bolo gosi, ka di
Harry dusukunnata barikama, juguba min tun b’a la k’a y’a su jisuma-nɛnɛ daga dɔ kɔnɔ dɔrɔn
ji.
A tun bɛ se ka Tabali Kɔrɔlen ye ka ɲɛ sisan. A laban na min ka surun a la, o sigilen tun bɛ
Hagrid, min y’a ɲɛ minɛ k’a bolokɔnincininw di a ma san fɛ. Harry ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ ka segin a kan.
Wa yen, Tabali sanfɛla cɛmancɛ la, sanu sigilan belebele dɔ kɔnɔ, Albus sigilen tun bɛ yen
Dumbledore ye a ka baara kɛ. Harry y'a dɔn o yɔrɔnin bɛɛ ka bɔ karti la a bɔra min kɔnɔ
Chocolat Frog bɛ tɛrɛn kɔnɔ. Dumbledore ka warijɛ kunsigi kelenpe de tun bɛ...
boon bɛɛ min tun bɛ yeelen bɔ i n’a fɔ jinɛw. Harry ye Karamɔgɔ Quirrell ye, san 1999.
fana, kamalennin jɔrɔlen min bɔra Leaky Cauldron la. A tun bɛ ka filɛli kɛ kosɛbɛ
kɛrɛnkɛrɛnnenya la, a bɛ kɛ finimugu belebeleba dɔ la min ɲɛ ye bulama ye.
Wa sisan, mɔgɔ saba dɔrɔn de tun tora ka tila. “Tɔmas, Dekan,” .
cɛden Numukɛ dɔ min janya tun ka bon ni Ron ye yɛrɛ, o farala Harry kan Gryffindor tabali la. “Turpin, .
Lisa,” a kɛra Ravenclaw ye o kɔfɛ, Ron ka waati sera. A tun ye pale green ye
sisan. Harry y’a bolokɔnincininw tigɛ tabali jukɔrɔ ani segin kelen o kɔfɛ, fini tun bɛ o la
a pɛrɛnna ko: “GRIFFINDOR!”
Harry ye a bolonɔ bila ni kanba ye ni tɔw ye tuma min na Ron binna sigilan kan min bɛ a kɛrɛfɛ
a.
Percy Weasley y’a fɔ ni yɛrɛbonya ye Harry fan bɛɛ fɛ ko: “I ka ɲi, Ron, a ka ɲi kosɛbɛ.”
iko “Zabini, Blaise,” kɛra Slytherin ye cogo min na. Karamɔgɔ McGonagall y’a kurukuru
scroll ani ka Sorting Hat ta ka taa.
Harry y’a ɲɛw jigin a ka sanu tasa lankolon na. A tun y’o faamu sisan dɔrɔn
kɔngɔ tun b'a la cogo min na. A tun bɛ iko pɔnpe pastiw tun bɛ san caman bɔ.
Albus Dumbledore tun sera a sen kan. A tun bɛ ka yeelen bɔ ka...
kalandenw , a bolow dabɔra kosɛbɛ , i n' a fɔ foyi tun tɛ se k' a diya ka tɛmɛ
k' u bɛɛ ye yen .
A ko: “Aw ni ce. “Aw ni ce san kura la Hogwarts! Sani an ka kɛ
an ka seli daminɛ , n b' a fɛ ka kuma damadɔ fɔ . Wa u filɛ nin ye: Nitwit!
Blubber (Blubber) ye! Oddment (ko kabakoma) don! Tweak (Tweak) kɛ!
"A' ni cɛ!"
A seginna ka sigi. Bɛɛ ye bolonɔ bila ani ka nisɔndiya. Harry tun t'a dɔn
a kɛra ŋɛɲɛ ye wo, a kɛra ŋɛɲɛ tɛ wo.
“Yala a — dibi don dɔɔnin wa?” a ye Percy ɲininka ni dannayabaliya ye.
"Fatɔ?" Percy y’o fɔ ni fiɲɛ ye. “A ye hakilitigi ye dɛ! Lagbɛrikɛla ɲumanba diɲɛ kɔnɔ! Nka
a bɛ dimi dɔɔnin, ɔwɔ. Pomitoro, Harry?”
Harry da wulila. Minɛn minnu tun bɛ a ɲɛfɛ, olu tun falen bɛ sisan
dumuni. A tun ma deli ka fɛn caman ye minnu ka di a ye ka dun tabali kelen kan: misisogo tobilen, .
sogo tobilen, donsokɛ tobilen ani sagaden tobilen, sosiso, bagan ani stɛki, tobilen
pɔmitɛri, pɔmitɛri tobilen, shɔ, Yorkshire pudding, pɔmutɛri, karɔti, shɔ, ketchup,
ani, kun kabakoma dɔw kosɔn, pepinɛri humbugs.
Dursley somɔgɔw tun ma deli ka kɔngɔ bila Harry la tigitigi, nka a tun ma deli ka kɔngɔ kɛ
a y' a to a ka dumuni kɛ i n' a fɔ a diyara a ye cogo min na . Dudley tun ye fɛn o fɛn ta tuma bɛɛ ko Harry
a tun b'a fɛ tiɲɛ na, hali n'a y'a bana. Harry y'a ka tasa dalajɛ ni dɔɔnin ye
fɛn bɛɛ fo pepinɛriw ka dumuni daminɛ. O bɛɛ tun ka di.
“O ɲɛ ka ɲi tiɲɛ na,” jinɛ min tun bɛ ruff kɔnɔ, o y’o fɔ ni dusukasi ye, k’a to Harry filɛli la
a y'a ka stɛki tigɛ.
“I tɛ se ka —?”
Jinɛ ko: “Ne ma dumuni kɛ a bɛ san kɛmɛ duuru ɲɔgɔn bɔ. "Ne tɛ
mago bɛ o la, tiɲɛ don, nka mɔgɔ bɛ to a la. N hakili la, n ma n yɛrɛ jira wa? cɛ
Nicholas de Mimsy-Porpington bɛ aw ka baara la. Gryffindor ka jinɛ sigilen
Sankanso.”
“Ne b’a dɔn i ye mɔgɔ min ye!” Ron y’o fɔ yɔrɔnin kelen. “Ne balimakɛw ye o ko fɔ n ye
i — i ye Nearly Headless Nick ye!”
“Ne b’a fɛ i ka ne wele ko Sir Nicholas de Mimsy —” jinɛ
a daminɛna ni gɛlɛya ye, nka Seamus Finnigan min kunsigi ye cɛncɛn ye, o y’a ka kuma tigɛ.
“A bɛ ɲini ka kɛ kunkolo tɛ min na wa? I bɛ se ka surunya kunkolo la cogo di?”
Sir Nicholas tun bɛ i ko a dusu tiɲɛna kosɛbɛ, i n’a fɔ u ka baro fitinin tɛ taa ɲɛ
a tun b'a fɛ cogo min na, o bɛɛ la.
A y’a fɔ ni dimi ye ko: “I n’a fɔ nin. A y'a kininbolo tulo minɛ k'a sama. A bɛɛ
kunkolo wulila ka bɔ a kɔ la ka bin a kamankun kan i n’a fɔ a bɛ fɛn dɔ kan.
A jɛlen don ko mɔgɔ dɔ tun y’a ɲini k’a kunkolo tigɛ, nka a ma o kɛ ka ɲɛ. Ka filɛli kɛ
a diyara u ɲɛda cogoya kabakomaw ye, Nearly Headless Nick y’a ta wuli
kunkolo segin a kɔ kan, ka sɔgɔsɔgɔ, k’a fɔ ko : “O tuma na fɛ — Grifindor kura ! N jigi b'a kan
aw bɛna an dɛmɛ ka so ka ntolatantɔn ŋanaya sɔrɔ ɲinan ? Gryffindors ye
a ma deli ka mɛn ten k’a sɔrɔ a ma se sɔrɔ. Slytherins ye tasa in sɔrɔ san wɔɔrɔ kɔnɔ a
mankan! Baron Jolilen bɛ ka kɛ fɛn ye min tɛ se ka muɲu — ale de ye Slytherin ye
ja."
Harry ye Slytherin tabali filɛ, a ye jinɛ jugu dɔ sigilen ye
yen, ɲɛ jɛlenw, ɲɛda nɔgɔlen, ani fini minnu nɔgɔlen don ni warijɛ joli ye.
A tun bɛ Malfoy kɛrɛfɛ yɛrɛ min, Harry diyara a ye k’a ye, a ma filɛli kɛ fana
sigiyɔrɔ labɛncogo diyara u ye.
“A datugulen don joli la cogo di?” Seamus ye ɲininkali kɛ ni kɔnɔnajɛyaba ye.
Nearly Headless Nick y’a fɔ ni kɔnɔnajɛya ye ko: “Ne ma deli ka ɲininkali kɛ.
Bɛɛ ye dumuni kɛ tuma min na u seko la, dumuni tolenw
a tun bɛ bɔ fasaw la, k’u to u saniyalen don ka manamana i n’a fɔ fɔlɔ. Dɔgɔkun kelen o kɔfɛ
desɛriw bɔra kɛnɛ kan. Glasi blokiw bɛ sɔrɔ a dafalen bɛɛ la i bɛ se ka miiri min na, .
pɔmi sɔgɔlenw, treacle tarts, chocolat eclairs ani jam donuts, trifle, fraises,
Jell-O, tiga pudding...
Harry y’a yɛrɛ dɛmɛ tuma min na ka treacle tart dɔ kɛ, jɛmukan jiginna u ka denbayaw ma.
Seamus ko: “Ne ye tilancɛ ni tila ye. “Ne fa ye Muggle ye. Mama ma o fɔ
ale a tun ye jatɔya ye 'til u furulen kɔfɛ. A kɛra fɛn juguba ye a bolo.”
Tɔɔw ye ŋɛɲɛ kɛ.
“E dun, Neville?” Ron y’o fɔ.
Neville ko: “Ayiwa, n kɔrɔkɛ ye n lamɔ ani a ye jatɔmuso ye, nka a
denbaya tun b’a miiri ko ne ye Muggle bɛɛ ye san caman kɔnɔ. N kɔrɔkɛba Algie tora k’a ɲini
ka n minɛ ka bɔ n ka kɔlɔsili la ka majigi dɔw wajibiya ka bɔ n na — a ye n gɛn ka bɔ
laban na Blackpool kurunboli yɔrɔ la siɲɛ kelen, n tun bɛ ɲini ka jigin — nka foyi ma kɛ fo n
tun ye mɔgɔ 8 ye. Uncle Algie nana lamini sufɛdumuni na, a tun bɛ ka n dulon
ka sanfɛla finɛtiri dɔ kɛ senkɔniw kɛrɛfɛ tuma min na n kɔrɔmuso Enid ye a di a ma
meringue ani a ye a bila ka bala. Nka ne ye bounce — ka jigin sira bɛɛ fɛ
nakɔ kɔnɔ ani ka don sira la. U bɛɛ nisɔndiyara tiɲɛ na, Gran tun bɛ kasi, a tun bɛ kasi
o nisɔndiyalen don kosɛbɛ. Wa i tun ka kan k’u ɲɛda ye tuma min na ne donna yan — u
miiri la, n’a sɔrɔ n tɛ se ka kɛ majigi ye ka na, i y’a ye. Uncle belebele Algie tun ye
a diyara a ye kosɛbɛ ka n ka wulu san ne ye.”
Harry fan dɔ fɛ, Percy Weasley ni Hermione tun bɛ ka kuma
kalanw (“Ne jigi b’a kan k’u bɛ daminɛ o yɔrɔnin bɛɛ, fɛn caman bɛ yen ka kalan, ne bɛ...
kɛrɛnkɛrɛnnenya la, a mago bɛ Transfiguration la, i b’a dɔn, ka fɛn dɔ tigɛli kɛ
fɛn wɛrɛ, tiɲɛ don, a ka kan ka gɛlɛya kosɛbɛ —”; “I bɛna kɛ
ka daminɛ fitinin na, a bɛ bɛn dɔrɔn ka kɛ pikirijikɛlanw ye ani o fɛn sugu — ”).
Harry, min tun bɛ ka a daminɛ ka funteni ni sunɔgɔ sɔrɔ, o ye a ɲɛ kɔrɔta ka Kɔrɔtalen filɛ
Tabali tuguni. Hagrid tun bɛ ka dɔlɔ min kosɛbɛ a ka jifilen na. Karamɔgɔ McGonagall ye o baara kɛ
tun bɛ ka kuma ni Karamɔgɔ Dumbledore ye. Karamɔgɔ Quirrell, a ka fini nalonma kɔnɔ, .
tun bɛ ka kuma karamɔgɔ dɔ fɛ, a kunsigi nɛrɛma tuluma, a nugu sirilen don, a fari tun ye bulama ye.
O kɛra yɔrɔnin kelen kosɛbɛ. Karamɔgɔ min nugu ye nɛgɛ ye, o ye a ɲɛw tɛmɛn
Quirrell ka finimugu tilennen don Harry ɲɛw la — ani dimi nɔgɔlen, funteniman dɔ ye marifa ci ka tɛmɛ
joginda min bɛ Harry ɲɛda la.
“Ouch!” Harry ye bolo dɔ da a kun na.
“O ye mun ye?” Percy ye ɲininkali kɛ.
“N-foyi tɛ.”
Dimi tun tɛmɛna joona i n’a fɔ a nana cogo min na. A tun ka gɛlɛn ka yɛrɛyɛrɛ ka bɔ a la, o tun ye...
dusukunnata Harry ye min sɔrɔ karamɔgɔ ɲɛda la — dusukunnata min tun man di a ye
Harry hali dɔɔnin.
“O karamɔgɔ bɛ ka kuma ni Karamɔgɔ Quirrell ye jɔn ye?” a ye Percy ɲininka.
“O, i bɛ Quirrell dɔn kaban, tiɲɛ tɛ? Kabako t'a la k'a filɛ o cogo la
nerveux, o ye Karamɔgɔ Snape ye. A bɛ Potions kalan, nka a t’a fɛ —
bɛɛ b' a dɔn ko a bɛ Quirrell ka baara kɔfɛ. A bɛ fɛn caman dɔn Dibi ko la
Seko ni dɔnko, Snape.”
Harry ye Snape kɔlɔsi waati dɔ kɔnɔ, nka Snape ma a filɛ tugun.
A laban na, dumunifɛnw fana tununna, karamɔgɔ Dumbledore sera o la
a senw tuguni. Salon makun.
