anw ye prefew ye. An filɛ nin ye.”
Kɔri laban yɛrɛ la, muso fasalenba dɔ ja tun dulonna a kɔnɔ
siliki fini pinki.
"Kɔdi?" a ko ten.
Percy ko: “Caput Draconis,” ja in wulila ka taa ɲɛfɛ walasa ka a jira
dingɛ bulama min bɛ kogo la. U bɛɛ ye ɲɔgɔn sɛgɛsɛgɛ a kɔnɔ — Neville mago tun bɛ sen na san fɛ
— ani u y’u yɛrɛ sɔrɔ Gryffindor common room kɔnɔ, so min ka di, a lamininen don
a falen bɛ sigilanw na minnu bɛ sɔgɔsɔgɔ.
Percy ye npogotigininw bila sira da kelen fɛ ka taa u ka siyɔrɔ la ani cɛdenw na
dɔ wɛrɛ sababu fɛ. Sanfɛla la, jirisunba dɔ — a jɛlen don k’u tun bɛ kelen kɔnɔ
sankansobaw — u y’u ka dilanw sɔrɔ laban na : jiribolo naani duuru sirilen bɛ ni bilenman jugumanba ye , .
velours ridow. U ka jirisunw tun lamɔna kaban. Sɛgɛn kojugu fo a tɛ se ka kuma
caman , u y' u ka pijamaw sama ka bin dilan kan .
“Dumuniba don, tiɲɛ tɛ?” Ron ye Harry sɔgɔsɔgɔ ka tɛmɛn fɛn sirilenw fɛ. "Sɔrɔ
off, Scabbers (Sɔgɔsɔgɔninjɛw)! A bɛ ne ka finiw ɲimi.”
Harry tun bɛna Ron ɲininka ni a ye treacle tart dɔ sɔrɔ, nka a binna
sunɔgɔ bɛ se ka kɛ siɲɛ kelen na.
N’a sɔrɔ Harry tun ye dumuni kɛ ka tɛmɛ dɔɔnin, bawo a tun ye dumuni kabakoma dɔ sɔrɔ kosɛbɛ
sugon. A tun bɛ Karamɔgɔ Quirrell ka fini don, o tun bɛ to ka kuma a fɛ,
k’a fɔ a ye ko a ka kan ka wuli ka taa Slytherin yɔrɔnin kelen, bawo o tun ye a ka siniɲɛsigi ye.
Harry y’a fɔ turban ye ko ale t’a fɛ ka kɛ Slytherin; a girinyana ka taa a fɛ ani
a ka gɛlɛn ka tɛmɛ; a y’a ɲini k’a sama ka bɔ nka a gɛlɛyara ni dimi ye — wa Malfoy tun bɛ yen,
ka ŋɛɲɛ kɛ a la k’a sɔrɔ a bɛ kɛlɛ kɛ n’a ye — o kɔfɛ, Malfoy y’i tigɛli kɛ karamɔgɔ nugulen ye, Snape, min ka ŋɛɲɛ kɛra sanfɛ ani nɛnɛ ye — pɛrɛn dɔ kɛra
yeelen jɛman ani Harry kununna, a sumana ani a yɛrɛyɛrɛla.
A y’i biri ka sunɔgɔ tugun, a kununna o dugujɛ tuma min na, a
hakili ma jigin o sugo la fewu .
