Filch ye.
U binna kɔfɛ — Harry ye da tugu, u bolila, u
a bɛ ɲini ka pan, ka segin ka jigin kɔri la. N’a sɔrɔ Filch ye teliya ka taa a ɲini
u bɛ yɔrɔ wɛrɛ la , bawo u m' a ye yɔrɔ si , nka u ka gɛlɛn
b’u janto — u tun b’a fɛ ka min kɛ dɔrɔn, o tun ye ka yɔrɔ caman bila u ni ɲɔgɔn cɛ
ani o waraba in. U ma boli dabila fo u sera ja la
Fat Lady bɛ sankanso wolonwulanan na.
“Aw bɛɛ taara min dugukolo kan?” a ye ɲininkali kɛ k'a ɲɛsin u ma
baarakɛminɛnw sirilen bɛ u kamankunw na ani u ɲɛda bilenmanw ni sumayalen.
“Aw kana o jate abada — donsokɛ nugu, donsokɛ nugu,” Harry ye fiɲɛ bila, ani ja in
a y’a yɛrɛ wuli ka taa ɲɛfɛ. U ye u yɛrɛ sɔgɔsɔgɔ ka don mɔgɔw ka so kɔnɔ ka bin,
yɛrɛyɛrɛli, ka don bololasigilanw kɔnɔ.
Waati dɔ tɛmɛna sani u si ma kuma. Neville, tiɲɛ na, a y’a filɛ
i n'a fɔ a tɛna kuma tugun abada.
“U hakili la u bɛ mun kɛ, ka o ɲɔgɔnna fɛn dɔ datugu
lakɔliso dɔ?” Ron y’o fɔ a laban na. “Ni wulu o wulu mago bɛ farikoloɲɛnajɛ la, o de mago bɛ o la.”
Erɔpumuso tun y’a ninakili ni a dimi jugu fila bɛɛ segin a ma tugun. "I
aw kana baara kɛ ni aw ɲɛw ye , aw si tɛ , tiɲɛ tɛ ?” a ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ. “I m’a ye o ye min ye wa
tun jɔlen bɛ a kan.
“Dugukolo kan?” Harry ye hakilina di. “Ne tun t’a senw lajɛ, ne fana tun bɛ
bolo degunnen a kunkolow la.”
“Ayi, duguma tɛ. A tun jɔlen bɛ janfa dɔ kan. A jɛlen don ko a bɛ kɔlɔsili kɛ
fɛn dɔ."
A wulila, k’u filɛ ni ɲɛmajɔ ye.
“Ne jigi b’a kan ko aw yɛrɛw bɛna diya aw ye. An bɛɛ tun bɛ se ka faga —
walima min ka jugu ni o bɛɛ ye, o ye ka gɛn ka bɔ yen. Sisan, n’i ma jɔrɔ, ne bɛ taa n da.”
Ron y’a ɲɛ jɔlen to a nɔfɛ, a da wulilen.
A ko: “Ayi, an t’a fɛ ka o kɛ. “I bɛna miiri ko an y’a sama ka taa, .
i tun tɛna o kɛ.
Nka Erɔpumuso tun ye fɛn wɛrɛ di Harry ma a ka miiri min na i n’a fɔ ale
a jiginna ka segin ka don dilan kan. Usi tun bɛ fɛn dɔ kɔlɔsi...Mun tun bɛ Hagrid la
fɔ? Gringotts tun ye yɔrɔ lakananen ye diɲɛ kɔnɔ fɛn dɔ kama i tun b’a fɛ min na
dogo — fo laala Hogwarts.
A kɛra i n’a fɔ Harry y’a dɔn o pake fitinin nɔgɔlen in bɛ yɔrɔ min na
ka bɔ vault kɛmɛ wolonwula ni tan ni saba tun ye.
HP 1 - Harry Potter ni a ka
Lagbɛrikɛla ka Kabakurun
SABABU TAN
HALLOWEEN KA ƝƐNABƆLI
M alfoy ma se ka da a ɲɛw la tuma min na a y’a ye ko Harry ni Ron bɛ yen
Hogwarts la o dugujɛ, a ɲɛda tun bɛ i ko a sɛgɛnnen don nka a nisɔndiyara kosɛbɛ. Tiɲɛ na, ka kɛɲɛ ni
o dugujɛ Harry ni Ron y’a miiri ko wulu kunkolo saba ye ɲɔgɔn sɔrɔ
kɛra ɲɛnajɛ ɲumanba ye, wa u tun b’a fɛ kosɛbɛ ka dɔ wɛrɛ sɔrɔ. Kɔnɔ
o waati kɔnɔ, Harry ye Ron fa pake ko la min tun bɛ iko a tun bɛ ten
bɔra Gringotts ka taa Hogwarts, wa u ye waati caman kɛ k’u yɛrɛ ɲininka mun na
a bɛ se ka kɛ ko a mago tun bɛ o lakanani gɛlɛn sugu la.
Ron ko: “A nafa ka bon tiɲɛ na walima farati bɛ a la tiɲɛ na.
Harry ko: “Wali u fila bɛɛ.
Nka i n’a fɔ u tun bɛ min dɔn tiɲɛ na o gundolafɛn in kan, o tun ye ko o de don
a janya bɛ se santimɛtɛrɛ fila ma, u ma se ka jateminɛ kɛ a ye min ye
k’a sɔrɔ taamasiyɛn wɛrɛw ma sɔrɔ.
Neville ni Hermione si ma u mago don hali dɔɔnin fɛn na min tun bɛ yen
wulu ni janfada jukɔrɔ. Neville tun b’a janto min na, o tun ye ko a tɛna taa abada
wulu kɛrɛfɛ tugun.
Hermione tun bɛ ban sisan ka kuma Harry ni Ron fɛ, nka a tun bɛ o cogo la
a bossy know-it-all ko u y'a ye ko nin ye bonus faralen ye. U tun b’a fɛ fɛn o fɛn na tiɲɛ na
sisan tun ye segincogo ye Malfoy la, wa u nisɔndiyara kosɛbɛ, o cogo kelen na
fɛn sera lɛtɛrɛ fɛ dɔgɔkun kelen ɲɔgɔn o kɔfɛ.
Ni wuluw tun bɛ ka woyo ka don Salonba kɔnɔ i n’a fɔ a delila ka kɛ cogo min na, bɛɛ hakili
minɛna o yɔrɔnin bɛɛ la pake jan finman dɔ fɛ min tun bɛ taa ni wuluba wɔɔrɔ ye minnu bɛ wele ko screech owls.
Harry tun b’a fɛ i n’a fɔ mɔgɔ tɔw bɛɛ k’a ye fɛn min bɛ nin parsela belebele in kɔnɔ,
a kabakoyara tuma min na wuluw wulila ka jigin k' a fili a ɲɛfɛ yɛrɛ .
k'a ka baganw gosi duguma. U tun ma wuli ka bɔ sira kan tuma min na
wulu wɛrɛ ye bataki dɔ fili parsela sanfɛ.
Harry ye bataki in tigɛtigɛ fɔlɔ, o kɛra hɛrɛ ye, bawo a ko:
AW KAN’A PARSELI DA ƝƐ TABULU LA.
I ka Nimbus Two Thousand kura bɛ a kɔnɔ, nka n t'a fɛ
bɛɛ k' a dɔn ko i ye bɔrɔsi sɔrɔ walima u bɛɛ bɛna dɔ fɛ. Oliver ye
Wood bɛna i kunbɛn bi su in na Quidditch kɛnɛ kan nɛgɛ kanɲɛ wolonwula waati i ka fɔlɔ kama
kalan kɛcogo.
Karamɔgɔ McGonagall ye o baara kɛ
A tun ka gɛlɛn Harry ma k’a ka nisɔndiya dogo tuma min na a tun bɛ o sɛbɛn di Ron ma walasa a k’a kalan.
“Nimbus ba fila!” Ron ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ ni keleya ye. “Ne ma deli ka hali
magara kelen na.”
U bɔra boon kɔnɔ joona, u tun b’a fɛ ka bɔrɔ da wuli u kelen na
sanni u ka kalan fɔlɔ ka kɛ , nka dondaw tilancɛ la u ye sira sɔrɔ
sanfɛla la, Crabbe ni Goyle ye barika sɔrɔ. Malfoy ye o pake minɛ Harry fɛ ani...
a y'a ye.
“O ye bɔrɔ ye,” a ko, k’a fili ka segin Harry ma ni ɲagami ye
keleya ni dusukasi min tun bɛ a ɲɛda la. “I bɛna kɛ a kɔnɔ nin siɲɛ in na, Potter, san fɔlɔw
tɛ sɔn u ma.”
Ron ma se ka a yɛrɛ tanga o ma.
A ko: “A tɛ bɔrɔ kɔrɔ si ye, a ye Nimbus Ba Fila ye.
I ko mun bɛ i bolo so, Malfoy, Comet Two Sixty?” Ron ye
a ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ Harry la. “Komɛtiw bɛ i ko u bɛ yeelen bɔ, nka u tɛ liigi kelen na ni...
Nimbus.”
“I tun bɛna mun dɔn o ko la, Weasley, i tun tɛ se ka tilayɔrɔba...
bololanɛgɛ,” Malfoy y’a kɔsegin ni sɔgɔsɔgɔ ye. “Ne hakili la, e n’i balimaw ka kan ka wari mara
jiribolo ni jiribolo.”
Sani Ron ka se ka jaabi di, Karamɔgɔ Flitwick y’a yɛrɛ jira Malfoy ka so
nɔnkɔnkuru.
“Ka sɔsɔli kɛ, ne jigi b’a kan, cɛdenw?” a ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ.
Malfoy y’a fɔ joona ko: “Bɔrɔsi cilen don Potter ma, Karamɔgɔ.”
Karamɔgɔ Flitwick y’a fɔ, k’a ɲɛji bɔ Harry la ko: “Ɔwɔ, ɔwɔ, o ye tiɲɛ ye.”
“Karamɔgɔ McGonagall ye o ko kɛrɛnkɛrɛnnenw bɛɛ fɔ n ye, Potter. Ani
o ye misali jumɛn ye?”
“Nimbus ba fila, o don,” Harry y’a fɔ, k’a kɛlɛ walasa a kana ŋɛɲɛ kɛ
siranɲɛ filɛli Malfoy ɲɛda la. “Wa tiɲɛ na, Malfoy de bɛ yan, ne ye o kɛ
y’a sɔrɔ », a y’o fɔ ka fara a kan.
Harry ni Ron taara sanfɛ, k’u ka ŋɛɲɛ dabila Malfoy ka so
dimi ni ɲagami jɛlen.
“Ayiwa, tiɲɛ don,” Harry ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ tuma min na u sera marbre sanfɛ
eskala la, “Ni a tun ma Neville ka Remembrall sonya ne tun tɛna kɛ ekipu kɔnɔ.
...”
“O la sa, ne hakili la, e fɛ, o ye sara ye sariyaw tiɲɛni na wa?” nana an
dimi kan bɔra u kɔfɛ dɔrɔn. Erɔpumuso tun bɛ ka senna-tɛgɛrɛ kɛ ka wuli eskala la, .
ka pake min bɛ Harry bolo, o filɛ ni a ma sɔn.
“Ne tun b’a miiri ko i tɛ kuma an fɛ wa?” Harry y’o fɔ.
Ron ko: “Ɔwɔ, kana jɔ sisan, o bɛ nafa caman lase an ma.”
Erɔpumuso taamana ka taa n’a nugu ye fiɲɛ na.
Harry ye gɛlɛya caman sɔrɔ k’a hakili to a ka kalanw na o don. A
tora ka yaala-yaala ka wuli ka taa siyɔrɔ la, a ka bɔrɔ kura dalen bɛ yɔrɔ min na
a ka dilan, walima ka bɔ Quidditch foro la a tun bɛna o tulon dege yɔrɔ min na
su. A y’a ka sufɛdumuni bolt o wula fɛ k’a sɔrɔ a m’a kɔlɔsi a bɛ min dun,
ka tila ka boli ka taa san fɛ ni Ron ye walasa ka Nimbus Ba Fila da wuli laban na.
“Wow,” Ron ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ, tuma min na bɔrɔsi bɛ ka wuli Harry ka dilan kan.
Hali Harry, min tun tɛ foyi dɔn balabala suguya ninnu na, o y’a miiri o la
a tun bɛ i ko kabako. A tun bɛ sɔgɔsɔgɔ ani a tun bɛ manamana, a bolo tun bɛ kɛ ni mahogani ye, a tun bɛ ni kɔ jan ye
jiribolo jɛlenw, tilennenw ani Nimbus Two Thousand sɛbɛnnen sanu na sanfɛ kɛrɛfɛ.
Ni nɛgɛ kanɲɛ wolonwula surunyana, Harry bɔra kaburu kɔnɔ ka taa sira minɛ wula fɛ
ka taa Quidditch foro fan fɛ. Held ma deli ka kɛ stade kɔnɔ fɔlɔ. Kɛmɛ kɛmɛ caman
sigiyɔrɔw tun bɛ kɔrɔta jɔyɔrɔw la foro lamini na walasa filɛlikɛlaw ka kɛ sanfɛ
ka se ka a lajɛ min tun bɛ sen na. Foro fan fila bɛɛ la, sanu saba tun bɛ yen
berew ni bɔrɔw bɛ u laban na. U ye Harry hakili jigin plastiki bere misɛnninw na
Muggle denmisɛnw tun bɛ bulonw fiyɛ ka tɛmɛ, fo n’u janya tun ye mɛtɛrɛ bi duuru ye.
A tun kɔrɔtɔlen don kojugu ka pan tugun ka Wood makɔnɔ, Harry y’a ka bɔrɔsi wuli
ka senna-tɛgɛrɛ kɛ ka bɔ duguma. Dusukunnata jumɛn don — a ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ ka don ka bɔ
gofɛrɛnaman ka bolo kan ka sɔrɔ ka teliya ka wuli ka jigin foro kɔnɔ. Nimbus Ba Fila
a y'i Yɛlɛma a b'a fɛ yɔrɔ o yɔrɔ a ka magali nɔgɔman na.
“Hee, Poyi, jigin!”
Oliver Wood tun sera yen. A tun bɛ ka jirisunba dɔ ta a jukɔrɔ
tɛgɛkala. Harry jigira a kɛrɛ fɛ.
Wood y’a fɔ, a ɲɛw bɛ ka manamana ko: “A ka di kosɛbɛ. “Ne b’a ye ko McGonagall
kɔrɔ tun ye...i ye natural ye tiɲɛ na. N b'aw kalan sariyaw la dɔrɔn nin
wula fɛ, o kɔfɛ, i bɛna fara ekipu degeliw kan siɲɛ saba dɔgɔkun kɔnɔ.”
A ye kɛsu da wuli. Kɔnɔna na, bololanɛgɛ naani tun bɛ yen minnu bonya tun tɛ kelen ye.
Wood ko: “Tiɲɛ don. “Sisan, Quidditch faamuyali ka nɔgɔn kosɛbɛ, hali
ni a ma nɔgɔn kojugu ka tulon kɛ. Furuɲɔgɔnma wolonwula bɛ yen fàn kelen-kelen bɛɛ la. U la saba
bɛ wele ko Chasers.”
“Tree Chasers,” Harry seginna a kan, tuma min na Wood ye bolo bilenman jɛman dɔ bɔ
a bonya bɛ se ntolatanbolo ma.
Wood ko: “Nin bolo in bɛ wele ko Quaffle. “Chasers bɛ fili
Quaffle ka ɲɔgɔn sɔrɔ k'a ɲini k'a tɛmɛ hoops dɔ fɛ walasa ka goal sɔrɔ.
Point tan tuma o tuma ni Quaffle bɛ tɛmɛ hoops dɔ fɛ. Aw ka tugu ne kɔ?”
“Chasers bɛ Quaffle fili k’a don hoops kɔnɔ walasa ka se ka kuru sɔrɔ,”
Harry ye kalan kɛ. “O la — o bɛ i n’a fɔ basikɛti min bɛ broomstick kan ni wɔɔrɔ ye
hoops, o tɛ wa?”
“Basket ye mun ye?” Wood y’o fɔ ni ɲininkali ye.
Harry y’a fɔ joona ko: “A kana kɛ abada.
“Sisan, ntolatanna wɛrɛ bɛ fan kelen-kelen bɛɛ la min bɛ wele ko Keeper — ne
