Bludgers (Bludgers) ye.
O yɔrɔnin bɛɛ, bololanɛgɛ nɛrɛma wulila sanfɛ fiɲɛ na, ka tila k’a yɛrɛ ci
Harry ka ɲɛda. Harry y’a wuli ni batɛmu ye walasa k’a bali k’a nugu kari, ani
a y’a ci ka zigzag ka taa fiɲɛ na — a ye zoom kɛ u kunkolo la o kɔfɛ
