ka lot. A minɛni ka gɛlɛn kosɛbɛ bawo a teliyalen don kosɛbɛ wa a yecogo ka gɛlɛn. O ye...
Seeker ka baara ka a minɛ. I ka kan ka siri ka don ka bɔ Chasers, Beaters, .
