a bɔra a ka se kɔrɔ pewu. A ma se k'a wuli. A tun tɛ se k’a ɲɛminɛ hali dɔɔnin. A
tun bɛ zigzag fiɲɛ fɛ, ani tuma ni tuma a tun bɛ swishing farimanw kɛ
lamaga-lamagali minnu tùn bɛ ɲini k'a Bɔ a sigiyɔrɔ la.
Lee tun bɛ ka ɲɛfɔli kɛ hali bi.
“Slytherin min bɛ a bolo — Flint ni Quaffle — o tɛmɛna Spinnet fɛ —
