tun ma diya ka tɛmɛn a cogo kɔrɔ kan kabini Quidditch ntolatan kɛra. A farinyalen don
ko Slitherinw ye bɔnɛ sɔrɔ, a tun y’a ɲini ka bɛɛ nisɔndiya cogo min na jirisunba dɔ bɛna kɛ Harry nɔ na ka kɛ Seeker nɔ ye o kɔfɛ. O kɔ, a tun y'a faamu
ko mɔgɔ si ma nin sɔrɔ nisɔndiyako ye , bawo u bɛɛ kabakoyara kosɛbɛ sira la
