kalanden minnu tun bɛna to seliw la, ani Harry tun y’a tɔgɔ sɛbɛn
siɲɛ kelen. A ma hinɛ a yɛrɛ la fewu; n’a sɔrɔ nin tun bɛna kɛ a bɛɛ la ɲuman ye
Noɛli a tun delila ka min kɛ. Ron n’a balimakɛw fana tun bɛ to yen, bawo Mr.
ani Madamu Weasley tun bɛ taa Rumani ka taa bɔ Charlie ye.
