HP 1 - Harry Potter ni a ka
Lagbɛrikɛla ka Kabakurun
SABABU TAN NI SABANAN
NICHOLAS FLAMEL KA ƝƐNABƆLI
D umbledore tun ye Harry lasun a kana taa Erised ka filɛlikɛlan ɲini
tugun, ani Nowɛli seli tɔw la, yebali fini tora
a dabɔra a ka jirisunba jukɔrɔ. Harry tun b’a fɛ a ka ɲinɛ a ye min ye kɔnɔ
filɛlikɛlan nɔgɔyara ten, nka a ma se. A y’a daminɛ ka sugo juguw kɛ. Ka tɛmɛn ani
a ye siko kɛ tugun a bangebagaw tununni yeelen jɛman dɔ kɔnɔ ,
k’a sɔrɔ kanba dɔ tun bɛ ka sɔgɔsɔgɔ ni nisɔndiya ye.
“I y’a ye, Dumbledore tun bɛ tiɲɛ fɔ, o filɛlikɛlan bɛ se k’i kɛ diɲɛnatigɛla ye,” a ko ten
Ron, tuma min na Harry ye nin sugo ninnu fɔ a ye.
Erɔpumuso min seginna ka na tile kelen sanni kalan ka daminɛ, o ye fɛɛrɛ wɛrɛ ta
fɛnw filɛli. A farala siran ni ɲɔgɔn cɛ Harry bɔli hakilina fɛ
dilan kan, ka yaala-yaala lakɔliso kɔnɔ su saba tugu-tugu ɲɔgɔn na (“Ni Filch tun y’i minɛ!”), ani
jigitigɛ min kɛra a la ko a ma dɔgɔya a la k’a dɔn Nicolas Flamel ye jɔn ye.
U tun bɛ ɲini ka jigiya dabila ko u bɛna Flamel sɔrɔ don dɔ gafemarayɔrɔ gafe dɔ kɔnɔ,
hali ni Harry tun dalen b'a la hali bi ko a bɛna o tɔgɔ kalan yɔrɔ dɔ la. Siɲɛ kelen term tun bɛ
daminɛna, u tun seginna ka gafew sɛgɛsɛgɛ miniti tan kɔnɔ u ka waati la
bɛ kari. Harry ka waati tun ka dɔgɔ hali ka tɛmɛ fila tɔw kan, bawo Quidditch dege
tun daminɛna kokura.
Wood tun bɛ baara kɛ ni ekipu ye kosɛbɛ ka tɛmɛn fɔlɔ kan. Hali sanji banbali min
tun ye nɛnɛ bila a nɔ na, ​​o ma se k'a hakili jigin. Weasleyw ye ŋunankan fɔ
ko Wood tun bɛ ka kɛ fanatic ye, nka Harry tun bɛ Wood fan fɛ. Ni u ye se sɔrɔ
u ka ntolatan nata, ni Hufflepuff ye, u tun bɛna Slytherin tɛmɛ so kɔnɔ
ka ntolatantɔn ŋanaya sɔrɔ a siɲɛ fɔlɔ la san wolonwula kɔnɔ. A ni a b’a fɛ ka se sɔrɔ, .
Harry y’a ye ko a tɛ sugo juguw kɛ dɔɔnin dɔɔnin ni a sɛgɛnnen don degeliw kɔfɛ.
O kɔfɛ, degeliw dɔ senfɛ kɛrɛnkɛrɛnnenya la, ji ni bɔgɔ la, Wood
ye kibaru jugu dɔɔnin di ekipu ma. A tun ye dimi kosɛbɛ Weasleyw fɛ dɔrɔn,
minnu tora ka dive-bombing kɛ ɲɔgɔn na ani k’a kɛ i n’a fɔ u bɛ bin u ka bɔrɔw kan.
“Yala i bɛna ɲagami dabila wa!” a pɛrɛnna. “O ye o sugu ye tigitigi
