Hagrid ye Harry ni Hermione minɛ k’u kɔrɔta ka bɔ sira kan kɔfɛ
jirisunba dɔ min ka bon kosɛbɛ. A ye bɛlɛkisɛ dɔ bɔ k’a don a ka jiribolo la, k’a kɔrɔta,
labɛnnen don ka tasuma don. U saba ye lamɛnni kɛ. Fɛn dɔ tun bɛ ka sɛgɛn ka tɛmɛn salen kan
furabuluw bɛ kɛrɛfɛ : a mankan tun bɛ i n’a fɔ fini min bɛ tugu duguma. Hagrid tun bɛ o cogo la
ɲɛjibɔ dibi sira kan, nka segin damadɔw tɛmɛnen kɔfɛ, mankan bɔra.
