ni dusukasi ye. “Tiɲɛ don, tugu ne kɔ, nka i janto i yɛrɛ la, sisan.”
U taamana dɔɔni dɔɔni, u tulo tun bɛ ka gɛlɛya walasa ka mankan fitiniba sɔrɔ. Yɔrɔni kelen,
yɔrɔ jɛlen dɔ kɔnɔ min bɛ ɲɛfɛ, fɛn dɔ jiginna sisan.
“Jɔn bɛ yen?” Hagrid ye wele kɛ. “A jira yerself — ne ye marifa ta!”
O yɔrɔ jɛlen na, a nana — yala cɛ don wa, walima sow? Ka se cɛsirilan ma, a
cɛ, kunsigi bilenman ni kunsigi tun b’a la, nka o jukɔrɔ, sow ka shɔni manamananan dɔ tun bɛ yen
farikolo min kùnkolo jan bɛ bilen. Harry ni Hermione ka dawolo jiginna.
