fɛn dɔw Changement de décoration de décoration dɔɔnin.”
A y'a bolow da. Yɔrɔnin kelen kɔnɔ, o fɛn jɛmanw kɛra bilenman ye
Warijɛ kɛra sanu ye. Slytherin sa belebeleba tununna ani sankanso dɔ
Gryffindor waraba y'a nɔ na. Snape tun bɛ ka Karamɔgɔ McGonagall bolo lamaga,
ni nisɔndiya juguba ye, min bɛ kɛ ni fanga ye. A ye Harry ɲɛ minɛ ani Harry y’o dɔn o yɔrɔnin bɛɛ
Snape dusukunnataw a ko la, o tun ma fɛn kelen Changé. O ma Harry jɔrɔ. A
a tun bɛ iko ɲɛnamaya bɛna segin a cogo kɔrɔ la san nata la, walima i n’a fɔ a tun bɛ cogo min na fɔlɔ
tun bɛ Hogwarts dugu la.
O kɛra Harry ka ɲɛnamaya wulada bɛɛ la ɲuman ye, min ka fisa ni se sɔrɔli ye Quidditch la,
walima Noɛli, walima ka kulu trolw gosi...a tun tɛna ɲinɛ abada, abada
su ni na.
Harry tun bɛ ɲini ka ɲinɛ ko ɛkizamɛn jaabiw tun ka kan ka na hali bi, nka na
u y'o kɛ. U kabakoyara kosɛbɛ k’a ye ko ale ni Ron fila bɛɛ tɛmɛna ni jate ɲumanw ye;
Tiɲɛ don, Erɔpumuso ye san fɔlɔw ka jate ɲumanw sɔrɔ. Hali Neville ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ
ka tɛmɛn, a ka Herbology taamasiyɛn ɲuman bɛ a ka abysmal Potions kelen kɛ. Olu
tun jigi b’a kan ko Goyle, min tun bɛ ɲini ka kɛ naloman ye i n’a fɔ a jugu, o bɛ se ka kɛ
filila kɛnɛma, nka a tun tɛmɛna, ale fana. O tun ye maloyako ye, nka i n’a fɔ Ron y’a fɔ cogo min na, i ma se
fɛn bɛɛ sɔrɔ ɲɛnamaya kɔnɔ.
Wa o yɔrɔnin bɛɛ, u ka finidoncogo lankolon don, u ka bagankuluw tun falen don, .
Neville ka wulu sɔrɔla a bɛ ka dogo ɲɛgɛnw nɔngɔn dɔ la; sɛbɛnniw tun bɛ tila-tila
ka kalandenw bɛɛ lasɔmi, k’u lasɔmi ko u kana baara kɛ ni jinɛweleli ye seli waatiw la (“ne jigi b’a kan tuma bɛɛ
u bɛna ɲinɛ ka ninnu di an ma,” Fred Weasley y’o fɔ ni dusukasi ye); Hagrid tun bɛ yen ka
aw k' u jigin kurunba kulu la minnu tun bɛ baji tigɛ ; u tun bɛ ten
ka don Hogwarts Express kurunba kɔnɔ; kuma ni ŋɛɲɛ bɛ kɛ cogo min na togodala kɛra cogo min na
ka ɲɛ ani ka labɛn ka ɲɛ; ka Bettie Bott ka Every Flavor Beans dun k’u to teliya la ka tɛmɛ
Muggle duguw; u ka lagbɛri finiw bɔli ani ka jakitew ni jatigila don;
ka sama ka don plateforme kɔnɔntɔn ni tila saba la Masakɛ ka Kuruwa Gara la.
A ye waati jan ta walisa u bɛɛ ka jigin plateforme kan. A wizened kɔrɔba
garadi tun bɛ san fɛ tikiti barika la, k'u bila ka tɛmɛ da la fila-fila ani
saba walasa u kana mɔgɔw hakili sama ni u bɛɛ pɛrɛnna ka bɔ kogo gɛlɛn dɔ la siɲɛ kelen
ani ka Muggles (Muggles) mɔgɔw lasiran.
Ron ko: “Aw ka kan ka na to yen ɲinan samiyɛ la, aw fila bɛɛ — ne bɛna o kɛ
i ka wulu dɔ ci i ma.»
Harry ko: “Barikama, ne mago bɛna kɛ fɛn na min bɛna makɔnɔ ni kɔnɔnajɛya ye.” Jama
y’u sɔgɔsɔgɔ k’u to ɲɛfɛ ka taa da la ka segin Muggle fɛ
duniya. U dɔw ye wele kɛ ko:
“Bye, Harry!”
“An bɛna ɲɔgɔn ye, Potter!”
Ron y’a fɔ k’a ɲɛji cɛ ko: “A tɔgɔ bɔra hali bi.
Harry ko: “Ne bɛ taa yɔrɔ min na, ne tɛ layidu ta i ye.
Ale ni Ron ani Hermione tɛmɛna da la ɲɔgɔn fɛ. “O yɔrɔ la, a
ye, Mama, a bɛ yen, a filɛ!”
Ginny Weasley tun don, Ron balimamuso dɔgɔmuso, nka a tun t’a bolo sin a ma
Ron ye.
“Hari Potter!” a ye sɔgɔsɔgɔ kɛ. “A filɛ, Mama! Ne bɛ se ka ye —”
“I makun, Ginny, wa a ye maloyako ye ka i bolo sin.”
Madamu Weasley ye nisɔndiya jira u la.
“San bolo degunnen don wa?” a ko ten.
Harry ko: “Kosɛbɛ. “Aw ni ce fudge ni sweater la, Madamu.
Weasley ye.”
“E, o tun tɛ foyi ye, n terikɛ.”
“I labɛnnen don wa?”
O tun ye Uncle Vernon ye, a ɲɛda tun ye bulama ye hali bi, a kunsigi tun bɛ a la hali bi, a ɲɛda tun bɛ i ɲɛ hali bi
diminnen Harry ka nɛrɛ la, a bɛ wulu dɔ ta kaburu kɔnɔ gare dɔ kɔnɔ min falen bɛ
mɔgɔ gansanw. A kɔfɛ, tantan Petunia ni Dudley jɔlen tun bɛ yen, u ɲɛda tun bɛ siran kosɛbɛ
Harry yecogo yɛrɛ.
“I ka kan ka kɛ Harry ka denbaya ye!” Madamu Weasley y’o fɔ.
Uncle Vernon ko: “Kunnafoni kɛcogo dɔ la. “Teliya, cɛnin, anw
ma tile bɛɛ sɔrɔ.” A taamana ka taa.
Harry y’a jɛngɛ ka segin ka kuma laban fɔ ni Ron ni Hermione ye.
“An bɛna ɲɔgɔn ye samiyɛ kɔnɔ, o tuma na fɛ.”
“Jigiya b’a la ko i ye — er — seli ɲuman sɔrɔ,” Erɔpumuso y’a fɔ k’a filɛ
siga t’a la Uncle Vernon kɔfɛ, a kabakoyara ko mɔgɔ o mɔgɔ bɛ se ka kɛ mɔgɔ ye min man di ten.
Harry ko: “O, ne bɛna o kɛ,” u kabakoyara sɔgɔsɔgɔninjɛ la min tun bɛ yen
ka jɛnsɛn a ɲɛda kan. “U t’a dɔn ko an man kan ka baara kɛ ni jinɛweleli ye at
so. N bɛna ɲɛnajɛ caman kɛ ni Dudley ye ɲinan samiyɛ la....
